title: A2141 820-01700 no power on
message:
Hi,

I have an A2141 820-01700 that doesn´t power on.

It puls 20V from ampmeter, but only 0.11A on all ports, and oscilates bettwen 0.4A and 0.13A (seams that it tries to boot and reboot) with battery disconected.

With battery connected it has the same behavier, but it goes  progressively until 0.70A and then 0.4A

Shall I try a DFU revive first?
